<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Falchion of the Koada'Vie Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
**Submitted by Chris B.**<BR>
<BR>
"The quest is as follows :<BR>
The Paladin Lord, Lord Jyleel, in the basement of the Paladin's guild wants you to [prove yourself a faithful paladin of the court]. He asks you to present him 3 things to prove this, and you shall wield "The falchion", a<BR>
paladin only weapon. Bring him the heart of Dvinn, find the supreme caster of the orcs, and also find the supply crate at the supply drop point from the orcs to the Tier'dal. Killing D'Vinn in Crushbone gets you his heart and<BR>
killing the orc prophet in Crushbone gets you a blue orc head.<BR>
<BR>
The crate is dropped by Brawn in the Ocean of Tears. He is about level 22 and spawns with 2 dark elf dragoons (approximately level 18 to 22)<BR>
on the rocks with the Sirens just as you enter the Ocean of Tears from Faydwer. Bring the items back to Lord Jyleel and he will give you a Falchion of the Koada'Vie."<BR>
</div>
<BR>
