It is a good weapon nevertheless and did until i got my ghoulbane.<BR>
If you really want one, you should easily be able to get the 2 items from crushbone if you hang around long enough...peopel are always killing dvinn and the prophet....as for the ogre..get a group and go hunting...remember tho..these items are NO DROP so make sure you are the one who loots the ogre fo rthe box..oh yes it weighs a TON!! so expect to be encumbered till you get to a bank.<BR>
Happy hunting<BR>
