<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Did this quest with some help from a couple Rising Phoenix members.  Brarm I think is the name of the Ogre. Yeah they may be around LVL 22 but they hit much higher also there are 3 dragoons Brarm and the Sirens will join in also, best to have someone who can levitate you along for the fight. The spawn is at 5 am every morning game time, he may be late. Also about 5 minutes after we had killed him they all spawned again.  <BR>
Nice weapon for a teen but after that go for a Crystalline or get your BIBS for 2HS.<BR>
