<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: </font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-15 22:18:51</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>As for getting Brawn to spawn on Siren Island.  Kill the middle siren and only the middle siren between 5 and 6 pm.  Brawn will spawn the next day and hopefully without the dragoons.  I have got the crate 3 times and it always works. The dragoons do have HT so watch out(maybe Brawn as well, but not really sure, cna't remember, oh well).  The crate weighs 20.  Do not kill any other sirens(they didn't agro on me, I was lvl 30 when I did it, hehe)because then the dragoons will spawn.</font></td></tr></table>
